{"tid":1712684,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於中大FA話水喉水有TG味","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T02:45:24.000Z","uid":80396,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a99ed8bb58ff2325701da8b02439b1d10a172b","tid":1712684,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"一。<span style=\"color: red;\">請先洗乾淨手臂手掌</span>，因為TG胡椒有機會殘留係身體，令人以為水有味<br />\n<br />\n二。<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量用地面至四樓既龍頭愈底愈好</span>。因為高層水經水缸，有少少機會會受TG污染。但地面通常都係直接供水，即係由配水庫直接供應到龍頭出水，污染機會低。<br />\n<br />\n三。<span style=\"color: red;\">避免接觸到龍頭出水咀</span>，因為可能會積聚污染物，從而污染食水。<br />\n<br />\n四。<span style=\"color: red;\">比水長流</span>。保持水喉水流動，就算有污染都可以衝走換水。"},{"pid":"ebc84afca72db30da9f048825ffb2e5bce219783","tid":1712684,"uid":205109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b97556e2d085b119ee5bf841e26d3d2f97f04565","tid":1712684,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4880c7c543358aca4ca23cc240c0ce911bf58a4d","tid":1712684,"uid":98826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"專業水喉佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf45e4fc9c5cf0a526ac6f5710d483a91a476418","tid":1712684,"uid":158496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f51483febdda1a810fd55f123af1b84795190972","tid":1712684,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d2995950e7fc8414499765e6f2f228730c4c7b","tid":1712684,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a